items.name: Renee Estella
items.description:
RenÃ¨e Estella is a model and social media personality with more than 800K followers on Instagram.

1000-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (r3nestella:0.99), a woman, RAW, close portrait photo, bodysuit with zipper, cleavage, fishnet stockings, pale skin, slim body, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3 sharp focus, f 5.6".

items.name: McLaren M14A Formula One (1970)
items.description:
Training notes:

V0.6 (SDXL) same "cooking" settings as the Ferrari 312 B v0.6 LoRA

V0.4 (SDXL) was trained on 38 imgs (x 4 repeats) with manually reviewed WD14 captions and 152 real 1970s formula one season photos as regularisation images, against sdXL_v10VAEFix model.

V0.2 (SDXL) FAT Bigger 1.7 GB version but generate more realistic images

Anyway for this vehicle I really need a better dataset with more hi-res pics

The McLaren M14A is a Formula One racing car built and raced by McLaren in the 1970 World Championship and the 1971 World Championship.

The M14A was an evolution of the previous M7A and M7C, with the primary change being the rear brakes were mounted inboard instead of outboard. As with the M7, the M14A was powered by a Cosworth DFV V8 and a Hewland 5-speed manual gearbox.

The unfortunate 1970s season began with two second places, one fourth and three retirements for Bruce McLaren and Denny Hulme.

items.description:
Honkai: Star Rail Video Game Graphics style LoRA

Making models can be expensive. Do you like what I do? Consider supporting me on Patreon ğŸ…¿ï¸ or feel free to buy me a coffee â˜•


After BotW and FF7Remake, another video game style. These look truly magical to me.

Should work fine at around weight 1 on AnyLoRA ckpt. Use honkai star rail style to increase fidelity.

Remember this is a style LoRA. To make characters accurately you need other networks too.

One of the examples is using my March 7th character LoRA and I also made a comparison image to show the difference.


How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight (by default it's :1 which is usually too high)

items.name: CROCHETED
items.description:
Crocheted refers to the art and technique of creating fabric using a hooked needle, known as a crochet hook, and yarn or thread. It is a versatile and popular craft that involves interlocking loops of yarn to form various patterns and designs.

Crocheted items can range from clothing and accessories, such as hats, scarves, and gloves, to home decor items like blankets, pillows, and decorative motifs. The possibilities are nearly endless, and crocheters can create a wide range of textures, shapes, and designs using different stitches and techniques.

Crocheting offers a sense of creativity and allows for personal expression through the choice of colors, patterns, and materials. It can be a relaxing and meditative activity, as well as a practical way to produce functional and beautiful items.

The process of crocheting typically involves creating a foundation chain of interconnected loops and then working different stitches to build the fabric. Common crochet stitches include single crochet, double crochet, and treble crochet, among many others. By combining these stitches and varying tension and yarn choices, crocheters can achieve different effects and textures in their work.

Crocheted items are often cherished for their warmth, softness, and handmade quality. They can be customized to fit individual preferences and can be made with a variety of yarn weights and fiber types, including cotton, wool, acrylic, and more.

Crocheting has a rich history and is practiced by people all over the world. It offers a creative outlet for individuals to express their artistic abilities and create unique and personalized items. Whether for practical use or decorative purposes, crocheted creations bring warmth, comfort, and a touch of handmade charm to our lives.

Rosalina LoHA | 5 Outfits in 1

This is a LoHA Lycoris and you need this Extension for this to work. My first LoHA Model and I'm happy with the results. Credits go to @EDG for helping me out. Thank you.

Weight can go from 0.7 up to 1.0. I recommend 0.9. ControlNet will streamline full body shots much easier, or more complex poses. Works with almost every Style, every alternative Outfit, Photorealistic Models and NSFW LoRA's.

You can also only use second trigger word, to give other Char Rosalina's Outfit (see example). If you wanna go for other Outfits for Rosalina, then use Rosalina_Casual, but it's optional.

This will be updated soon with other Outfits from Rosalina. I saw Sommer Outfit and some other Outfits in Mario Kart Tour. This will be included in the next Update.

I noticed a lack of Vanny from Security breach here, so I decided to give it a go as my first LoRA, I apologize for any inconsistencies as it is my first project. I welcome any and all suggestions/help/tips you have!

prompting "Vanny, patchwork costume, bunny costume, blue bow" gives a likely summon, however the pupils tend to be a bit unruly, which will generally require a few generations. "black pupils" might help a tad

You can use "broken costume" or "open costume" to do NSFW, or "Anthro" to attempt it without human skin.

Preview images were generated using "anyloraCheckpoint", latest "Kavkamix", "Toonify" and "CrossKemonoFurryModel"
